Notes

Vulpowder is a re-named Alolan Vulpix. In Pokemon Voyager, the Alola region was destroyed centuries ago, but some of its regional variants remain.

Ninefluffs is a re-named Alolan Ninetales. In Pokemon Voyager, the Alola region was destroyed centuries ago, but some of its regional variants remain.

Evolution
Pokedex

Egg group - FIELD

It can freely control fire, making fiery orbs fly like will-o'-the-wisps. Just before evolution, its six tails grow hot as if on fire.
It has long been said that each of the nine tails embody an enchanted power. A long-lived Ninefluffs will have fur that shines like gold.
